%20her%20training%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20UPSC%20also%20decided%20to%20use%20facial%20recognition%20and%20artificial%20intelligence-based%20CCTV%20surveillance%20systems%20to%20prevent%20cheating%20and%20impersonation%20in%20its%20various%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20tender%20document%2C%20it%20invited%20bids%20from%20experienced%20public%20sector%20undertakings%20to%20devise%20two%20tech%20solutions%20--%20%26quot%3BAadhaar-based%20fingerprint%20authentication%20(else%20digital%20fingerprint%20capturing)%20and%20facial%20recognition%20of%20candidates%20and%20QR%20code%20scanning%20of%20e-admit%20cards%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BLive%20AI-based%20CCTV%20surveillance%20service%26quot%3B%20--%20to%20be%20used%20during%20the%20examination%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20conducts%2014%20major%20exams%20annually%2C%20including%20the%20prestigious%20civil%20services%20examination%20to%20select%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%2C%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20(IFS)%20and%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%2C%20besides%20a%20number%20of%20recruitment%20tests%20and%20interviews%20every%20year%20for%20induction%20to%20Group%20'A'%20and%20Group%20'B'%20posts%20of%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakhs%20of%20candidates%20appear%20in%20such%20recruitment%20conducted%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724897760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqui9afrg_upsc_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcentre-allows-upsc-to-perform-aadhaar-based-authentication-for-candidates-verifications-6441616%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20assumes%20significance%20as%20the%20commission%20last%20month%20cancelled%20the%20p