ed%20the%2010th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Invictus%20Games.%20According%20to%20a%20source%20who%20spoke%20to%20People%2C%20Kettler%20was%20hired%20on%20a%20trial%20basis%2C%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20part%20ways%20was%20mutual%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20agreeing%20it%20wasn't%20the%20right%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20exit%20occurred%20just%20before%20the%20Sussexes'%20trip%20to%20Colombia%20this%20week%2C%20where%20they%20were%20scheduled%20to%20visit%20Bogota%2C%20Cartagena%2C%20and%20Cali.%20Colombia's%20Vice%20President%20Francia%20Marquez%20announced%20on%20August%201%20that%20the%20couple%20would%20meet%20with%20youth%20leaders%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20anti-online%20bullying%20campaign%2C%20a%20trip%20Mr%20Kettler%20had%20been%20expected%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ms%20Markle's%20delivery%20of%20strawberry%20jam%20jars%20to%20a%20select%20number%20of%20celebrities%20in%20March%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20business's%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20start.%26quot%3B%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20two%20has%20hinted%20at%20a%20potential%20rose%20wine%20line%20and%20sent%20dog%20biscuits%20to%20her%20celebrity%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20brand%20was%20unveiled%20through%20a%2016-second-long%20retro-style%20video%2C%20showing%20hands%20arranging%20flowers%2C%20and%20the%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex%20stirring%20a%20pot%20in%20a%20kitchen.%20It%20concluded%20with%20a%20glimpse%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20ball%20gown%20standing%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20long%20colonnade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20official%20American%20Riviera%20Orchard%20Instagram%20page%20included%20nine%20enlargements%20of%20close-up%20photos%20that%20collectively%20comprise%20the%20emblem.%20Its%20bio%20also%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20written%20%26quot%3Bby%20Meghan%2C%20The%20Duchess%20of%20Sussex.%20Established%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724897280000%