0tried%20his%20best%20during%20Wednesday's%20closely%20watched%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-call-live-updates-nvda-stock-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20he%20couldn't%20expunge%20these%20doubts%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20third-quarter%20revenue%20forecast%20didn't%20help.%20It%20missed%20so-called%20whisper%20numbers%20that%20represent%20the%20most%20bullish%20expectations.%20That%20left%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-questions-product-delays-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20stock%20down%207%25%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20peppered%20the%20CEO%20with%20questions%20about%20the%20return%20on%20AI%20spending.%20His%20response%20was%20several%20versions%20of%3A%20%26quot%3Bthe%20people%20who%20are%20investing%20in%20Nvidia%20infrastructure%20are%20getting%20returns%20on%20it%20right%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Nvidia's%20largest%20customers%20have%20yet%20to%20boast%20significant%20return%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-big-tech-spending-on-ai-investments-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillions%20in%20AI%20investing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Huang%20drilled%20down%20on%20several%20places%20he%20sees%20profits%20coming%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f3b3919-3f45-421e-8586-349f7550ac60%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGPUs%20speed%20everything%20up%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccelerated%20computing%2C%20of%20course%2C%20speeds%20up%20applications.%20It%20also%20enables%20you%20to%20do%20computing%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%2C%20for%20example%2C%20scientific%20simulations%20or%20database%20processing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Huang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccelerated%20computing%26quot%3B%20is%20Huang's%20term%20for%20the%20kind%20that%20Nvidia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgpu-rich-vs-gpu-poor-tech-companies-in-each-group-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egraphics%20processing%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20enable.%20It's%20also%20called%20parallel%20computing%20where%20the%20chips%20do%20many%20tasks%20simultaneously%20instead%20of%20in%20a%20sequence.%20That's%20the%20foundation%20of%20generative%20AI%20and%20Huang%20contended%20that%20almost%20all%20existing%20computing%20jobs%20are%20headed%20in%20that%20direction%20for%20one%20major%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20unusual%20to%20see%20someone%20save%2090%25%20of%20their%20computing%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20convert%20to%20accelerated%20computing%2C%20Huang%20said.%20The%20reason%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Byou%20just%20sped%20up%20an%20application%2050x.%20You%20would%20expect%20the%20computing%20cost%20to%20decline%20quite%20significantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229da5dd6e-12c1-4d9c-b134-83e8d285e801%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsumer%20targeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERecommendation%20engines%2C%20like%20the%20ones%20that%20tell%20you%20what%20to%20stream%20next%2C%20and%20digital%20ad%20targeting%2C%20were%20two%20modern%20data-processing%20tasks%20that%20are%20converting%20fast%20to%20accelerated%20computing%2C%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheaper%2C%20more%20accurate%20recommendations%20and%20better-targeted%20or%20ads%20could%20generate%20more%20revenue%20for%20companies%20that%20adopt%20those%20technologies.%20Meta%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20turbo-charged%20profit%20in%20recent%20years%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20improve%20content%20recommendations%20and%20ad%20targeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESophia%20Velastegui%2C%20a%20venture%20capitalist%20and%20former%20Microsoft%20AI%20executive%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20identifying%20the%20return%20on%20AI%20investments%20may%20not%20be%20easy%20as%20it%20gets%20baked%20into%20these%20everyday%20functions%20of%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20be%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20this%20growth%20is%20specifically%20from%20generative%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Velastegui%20said.%20She%20added%20that%20companies%20may%20not%20be%20keen%20to%20reveal%20the%20details%20of%20their%20AI%20gains%20for%20competitive%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22499f3ea9-5c90-423d-97dc-8a11629164c5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20AI%20cloud%20wave%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20third%20pillar%20of%20AI%20ROI%2C%20at%20least%20for%20cloud%20providers%2C%20is%20the%20startup%20development%20frenzy%20across%20generative%20AI%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20cloud-computing%20providers%2C%20including%20Amazon%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20are%20major%20customers%20of%20Nvidia.%20When%20they%20buy%20GPUs%2C%20they%20put%20them%20in%20data%20centers%20and%20get%20paid%20relatively%20quickly%20for%20renting%20out%20this%20new%20AI%20computing%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20you%20stand%20up%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20get%20rented%20because%20so%20many%20companies%20are%20being%20founded%20to%20create%20generative%20AI%20and%20so%20your%20capacity%20gets%20rented%20right%20away%2C%20and%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20of%20that%20is%20really%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20propelled%20a%20slew%20of%20new%20or%20reimagined%20cloud%20providers%20that%20purchase%20chips%20almost%20exclusively%20from%20Nvidia%20and%20specialize%20in%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest%20in%20AI%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20going%20to%20be%20difficult%20to%20assuage%20investors%20concerns%20in%20this%20area%20because%20ultimately%2C%20Huang%20isn't%20the%20executive%20they%20need%20to%20hear%20the%20message%20from.%20And%20what%20they've%20heard%20from%20other%20top%20tech%20execs%2C%20and%20top%20Nvidia%20customers%2C%20is%20calls%20for%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20spent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%2