or%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fmethodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20life%20insurance%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Angie%20Chatman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ccf43a1aa2ac29ee34748e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Angie%20Chatman.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Angie%20Chatman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWith%20lifespans%20longer%20and%20families%20more%20spread%20out%2C%20it's%20essential%20that%20I%20think%20about%20long-term%20care.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELong-term%20care%20insurance%20comes%20in%20many%20forms%20at%20many%20costs%2C%20including%20as%20part%20of%20a%20life%20insurance%20policy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20hope%20to%20have%20a%20long%2C%20comfortable%20life%2C%20but%20I'm%20preparing%20for%20whatever%20is%20ahead.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20was%20one%20of%2011%20children%2C%20three%20male%20and%20eight%20female.%20All%20but%20two%20lived%20and%20worked%20within%2050%20miles%20of%20where%20they%20grew%20up.%20When%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20grew%20ill%2C%20one%20of%20his%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20divorced%20and%20with%20a%20young%20son%20%E2%80%94%20moved%20in%20to%20care%20for%20each%20of%20them%20until%20they%20died.%20That%20was%20the%20norm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20norm%20no%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20are%20having%20fewer%20children.%20According%20to%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworldpopulationreview.com%2Fstate-rankings%2Faverage-household-size-by-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorld%20Population%20Review%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20household%20size%20in%20the%20United%20States%20is%202.6.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20living%20longer%20than%20past%20generations.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.health.harvard.edu%2Fblog%2Fwhy-life-expectancy-in-the-us-is-falling-202210202835%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20life%20expectancy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20women%20is%2079%20years%2C%20and%20for%20men%2C%2073%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20extended%20family%20is%20more%20dispersed.%20The%20average%20American%20changes%20residences%20every%20five%20years%2C%20although%20that%20trajectory%20has%20shifted%20now%20that%20more%20work-from-home%20options%20have%20become%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20days%20of%20an%20unmarried%20woman%20taking%20care%20of%20elderly%20relatives%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%20which%20is%20why%20long-term%20care%20insurance%20products%20%E2%80%94%20and%20long-term%20care%20riders%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20more%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227135d923-509b-47ad-8045-7ab31ff005bf%5C%22%3EWithout%20insurance%2C%20I%20can't%20afford%20long-term%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELong-term%20care%20includes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20services%2C%20from%20nursing%20homes%20and%20assisted%20living%20(out-of-home%20care)%20to%20licensed%20nurses%20and%20certified%20home%20health%20aides%20(in-home%20care).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20home%20state%20of%20Massachusetts%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20out-of-home%20care%20in%20a%20private%2C%20Medicare-certified%20facility%20can%20be%20as%20high%20as%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year.%20For%20in-home%20care%2C%20at%20two%20hours%20per%20day%2C%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20the%20cost%20would%20be%20%248%2C000%20a%20year.%20Medicare%20only%20covers%20a%20maximum%20of%20100%20days%20after%20a%20hospital%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnless%20we%20win%20the%20lottery%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20can't%20afford%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20begin%20discussing%20LTC%20with%20my%20clients%20when%20they're%20in%20their%20mid-50s%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Robert%20Kircher%2C%20a%20financial%20advisor%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fnorthwestern-mutual-life-insurance-review%5C%22%3ENorthwestern%20Mutual%20Insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20at%20that%20stage%20when%20the%20kids%20are%20(mostly)%20out%20of%20the%20house%20and%20there's%20room%20to%20consider%20what's%20next.%20Given%20life%20expectancy%20projections%2C%20what's%20next%20could%20be%20another%2025-30%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228915d9c2-a88b-4604-b12a-182eb31647e6%5C%22%3EI%20have%20lots%20of%20options%20for%20long-term%20care%20insurance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20projected%20future%20could%20be%20an%20active%20lifestyle%20filled%20with%20good%20health%2C%20friends%2C%20travel%2C%20and%20volunteer%20work%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20quick%20and%20painless%20death.%20What's%20more%20likely%20is%20a%20slow%20decline%20in%20physical%20and%20cognitive%20health%20with%20professional%20home%20health%20aides%20and%20skilled%20nurses%20assisting%20with%20personal%20hygiene%20and%20other%20daily%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong-term%20care%20insurance%20goes%20beyond%20the%20standard%20healthcare%20insurance%20policy.%20A%20long-term%20care%20insurance%20policy%20protects%20against%20the%20risk%20of%20having%20to%20pay%20out%20of%20pocket%20for%20in-home%20and%2For%20out-of-home%20care%20services.%20As%20with%20other%20insurance%20products%2C%20the%20amount%20you%20pay%20in%20premiums%20varies%20according%20to%20the%20amount%20of%20your%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20life%20insurance%20plans%20include%20a%20long-term%20care%20benefit%2C%20a%20death%20benefit%20when%20you%20pass%20away%2C%20and%20a%20cash%20value%20if%20you%20stop%20the%20policy.%20The%20advantage%20to%20this%20type%20of%20plan%20is%20you%20know%20your%20benefactors%20get%20all%20or%20most%20of%20the%20money%20you%20spent%20on%20premiums%20returned%20if%20you%20pass%20with%20no%20claim%2C%20but%20the%20tradeoff%20is%20a%20lower%20benefit%20amount.%20Still%20other%20products%20offer%20a%20full%20death%20benefit%20of%20the%20entire%20amount%2C%20but%20those%20plans%20have%20substantially%20higher%20premiums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22531ddf2b-63e5-49ac-b606-ad45f5c6bea1%5C%22%3EI'm%20taking%20steps%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20live%20a%20good%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%20long%20I%20may%20live%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20as%20healthy%20as%20I%20can%20during%20them.%20That%20means%20doing%20the%20work%20to%20stay%20healthy.%20I%20keep%20up%20with%20regular%20checkups%20with%20doctors%20and%20dentists%2C%20mammograms%20and%20colonoscopies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20avoid%20fast%20food.%20Instead%2C%20I%20cook%20most%20meals%2C%20which%20include%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20fresh%20vegetables%2C%20and%20snack%20on%20fruit%20rather%20than%20cookies%2C%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20I%20do%20yoga%20and%20take%20long%20walks.%20I%20have%20an%20active%20social%20life%20filled%20with%20good%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%20and%20the%20long%20run%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20live%20long%20and%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF