%20of%20the%20quickest%20and%20most%20affordable%20toasters%20we%20tested%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider%20may%20earn%20an%20affiliate%20commission.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-reviews-expertise-in-product-reviews%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELearn%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20original%20graphic%20of%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20Toaster%20on%20a%20gradient%20orange%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf4217397a16897201fb5b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDash%20is%20known%20for%20budget-friendly%20appliances%2C%20and%20we%20love%20the%20brand's%20ClearView%20Toaster.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20impatient%20in%20the%20kitchen%20and%20have%20been%20known%20to%20hit%20%26quot%3Bcancel%26quot%3B%20on%20my%20slot%20toaster%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20my%20slice%20of%20sourdough%20isn't%20getting%20too%20dark.%20Not%20only%20do%20I%20want%20an%20even%20toast%2C%20but%20I%20want%20it%20quickly%20and%20without%20the%20risk%20of%20burning.%20When%20I%20tested%20the%20best%20long-slot%20toasters%2C%20I%20found%20a%20budget%20model%20that%20satisfied%20my%20requirements%3A%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20Toaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDash%20incorporated%20a%20window%20into%20the%20front%20of%20the%20toaster%20so%20you%20can%20monitor%20your%20bagel%2C%20frozen%20bread%2C%20and%20more.%20Plus%2C%20it%20retails%20for%20under%20%2460.%20You%20won't%20always%20get%20a%20picture-perfect%20golden%20brown%2C%20but%20for%20the%20price%2C%20you%20can't%20be%20the%20Dash%20ClearView.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3EDesign%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223301%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Dash%20ClearView%20Long%20Slot%20Toaster%20with%20a%20slice%20of%20bread%20inside%2C%20showing%20the%20clear%20front%20window.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf30e3397a16897201e7b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222476%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThanks%20to%20a%20clear%20front%20window%2C%20you%20can%20monitor%20your%20toast%20in%20real%20time.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Tobin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20slot%20toasters%2C%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20is%20simple%20to%20set%20up%3A%20take%20it%20out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20remove%20cardboard%20spacers%20and%20protective%20stickers%2C%20plug%20it%20in%2C%20and%20you're%20ready%20to%20go.%20The%20toaster%20has%20a%20compact%20and%20streamlined%20silhouette%3B%20even%20if%20you%20have%20limited%20counter%20space%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20tuck%20into%20a%20corner%20or%20store%20in%20a%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exterior%20is%20covered%20by%20a%20plastic%20shield%20that%20comes%20in%20five%20colors.%20Not%20only%20can%20you%20match%20your%20decor%20or%20other%20appliances%2C%20but%20we%20found%20that%20the%20plastic%20doesn't%20scratch%20or%20show%20fingerprints%20as%20easily%20as%20stainless%20steel.%20You%20can%20wipe%20down%20the%20exterior%20with%20a%20damp%20cloth%20and%20gentle%20dish%20soap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20notable%20design%20attribute%20of%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20is%20in%20the%20name%3A%20a%20transparent%20window%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20toaster%20lets%20you%20watch%20the%20browning%20process.%20Anyone%20prone%20to%20accidentally%20over-toasting%20will%20be%20grateful%20for%20the%20ClearView%20window%3B%20you%20can%20use%20the%20built-in%20timer%20and%20your%20own%20judgment.%20The%20ClearView%20window's%20glass%20can%20be%20removed%20for%20a%20deep%20clean%20with%20warm%2C%20soapy%20water%20and%20a%20soft%20sponge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Toasting%5C%22%3EToasting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221231%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20slices%20of%20toast%20resting%20on%20top%20of%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20Long%20Slot%20Toaster.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf2e18397a16897201e60a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20tested%20alongside%20other%20similar%20models%20on%20the%20market%2C%20the%20DASH%20ClearView%20performed%20more%20quickly%20than%20all%20but%20two%20of%20the%20seven%20toasters%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Tobin%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tested%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20Toaster%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20by%20its%20toasting%20speed.%20In%20just%20two%20minutes%2C%20I%20got%20a%20midlevel%20toast%20(a%203.5%20on%20the%20ClearView's%20one%20to%20seven%20range)%20for%20room-temperature%20bread.%20A%20bagel%20took%20just%20slightly%20longer%20to%20reach%20medium%20brown%20(two%20minutes%20and%2020%20seconds)%2C%20and%20a%20slice%20of%20frozen%20bread%20hit%20the%20mark%20at%20two%20minutes%20and%2035%20seconds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20it%20doesn't%20toast%20very%20evenly.%20I%20noticed%20patchy%20areas%20of%20darker%20and%20lighter%20brown%20on%20all%20three%20bread%20types%20(room%20temperature%2C%20frozen%2C%20and%20bagel).%20If%20uniformity%20is%20a%20big%20priority%20for%20you%2C%20then%20this%20model%20may%20not%20be%20the%20right%20choice.%20But%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20love%20a%20quick%20toaster%20that%20gets%20the%20job%20done%20(albeit%20imperfectly)%2C%20the%20Dash%20ClearView%20Toaster%20is%20a%20quality%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Features%5C%22%3EFeatures%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20traditional%20push%20lever%20on%20the%20side%20is%20the%20toaster's%20main%20control.%20At%20the%20lower%20right%20corner%20of%20the%20ClearView%20window%2C%20you'll%20find%20a%20knob%20with%20a%20%26quot%3BCancel%26quot%3B%20button%20at%20the%20center.%20The%20knob%20can%20be%2