0quite%20some%20time.%20So%20there's%20%3Cem%3Esomething%3C%2Fem%3E%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20Trump's%20stock%20may%20be%20moving%20down%20is%20that%20lots%20of%20people%20who%20own%20Trump%20stock%20are%20Trump%20fans%2C%20and%2For%20people%20betting%20that%20Trump%20will%20win%20the%20November%20election.%20But%20it%20has%20been%20harder%20to%20be%20in%20one%20of%20those%20groups%20recently%3A%20Since%20Kamala%20Harris%20replaced%20Joe%20Biden%20as%20Trump's%20opponent%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnate-silver-kamala-harris-donald-trump-prediction-risk-book-interview-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20has%20been%20losing%20ground%20in%20the%20polls%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20now%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2024%2Fus%2Felections%2Fpolls-president.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natesilver.net%2Fp%2Fnate-silver-2024-president-election-polls-model%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epollster%20Nate%20Silver%3C%2Fa%3E%20see%20him%20as%20a%20slight%20underdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20DJT%20is%20a%20proxy%20for%20Trump's%20election%20chances%2C%20it%20would%20make%20sense%20that%20it%20has%20been%20limping%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20very%20plausible%20reason%20that%20Trump%20stock%20is%20moving%20down%20is%20that%20investors%20may%20be%20worried%20about%20Trump%20selling%20some%20of%20his%20shares%20in%20the%20company.%20This%20could%20lead%20to%20other%20investors%20selling%2C%20which%20would%20have%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20the%20share%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20currently%20owns%20about%2060%25%20of%20Truth%20Social%2C%20which%20means%20his%20stake%20is%20worth%20about%20%242.4%20billion.%20He's%20been%20restricted%20from%20selling%20any%20shares%20because%20of%20a%20lock-up%20restriction%2C%20which%20are%20common%20in%20public%20offerings.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F08%2F22%2Ftrump-djt-stock-sell-off-media.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20lock-up%20period%20could%20end%20as%20soon%20as%20September%2020%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20hence%20people%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20stock%20before%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20arguments%20against%20that%20theory%2C%20by%20the%20way%3A%20The%20first%20is%20that%20the%20lock-up%20period%20has%20been%20public%20knowledge%20since%20Truth%20Social%20first%20went%20public%2C%20so%20why%20bail%20now%3F%20The%20second%20is%20that%20Trump%20knows%20that%20if%20he%20does%20sell%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20and%20particularly%20if%20he%20sells%20a%20lot%20of%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20stock%20will%20%3Cem%3Ereally%3C%2Fem%3E%20collapse.%20Because%20all%20but%20the%20most%20die-hard%20Trump%20fans%20will%20see%20it%20as%20the%20end%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20there's%20a%20real%20tension%20there%3A%20Does%20Trump%20keep%20his%20theoretical%20%242.4%20billion%20stake%20intact%3F%20Or%20does%20he%20try%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20actual%20money%2C%20and%20risk%20making%20the%20overall%20value%20much%20less%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20both%20of%20the%20ideas%20above%20%E2%80%94%20Trump's%20declining%20political%20fortune%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20he%20may%20be%20ready%20to%20trigger%20a%20big%20sell-off%20himself%20%E2%80%94%20are%20true.%20Or%20maybe%20there's%20something%20else%20at%20work%20that%20we%20have%20yet%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20we%20know%20for%20certain%20is%20that%20if%20you%20bought%20Trump%20stock%20in%20late%20March%20and%20haven't%20sold%20it%20since%20then%2C%20you%20are%20down%20by%20more%20than%2050%25.%20We%20don't%20give%20investment%20advice%20around%20here.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-stock-price-crash-spac-djt-truth-social-2024-4%5C%22%20t