3EAs%20a%20travel%20editor%20(i.e.%2C%20professional%20traveler)%2C%20I%20take%20luggage%20personally.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-luggage%5C%22%3Ebest%20luggage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-carry-on-bag%5C%22%3Ecarry-on%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20not%20only%20be%20easy%20to%20whisk%20through%20airports%2C%20but%20also%20durable%2C%20spacious%2C%20and%20hopefully%20stylish.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20an%20ideal%20world%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20even%20notice%20you're%20lugging%20your%20luggage%2C%20because%20it%20transports%20and%20organizes%20your%20belongings%20so%20seamlessly.%20It%20should%20also%20be%20durable%3A%20I%20can't%20count%20how%20many%20times%20I've%20had%20suitcase%20wheels%20decide%20to%20stop%20working%20a%20few%20days%20into%20an%20international%20trip%2C%20or%20have%20opened%20my%20bag%20at%20my%20destination%20to%20find%20everything%20in%20total%20disarray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETired%20of%20single-use%20suitcases%20that%20made%20traveling%20even%20more%20painful%20(delays%20are%20bad%20enough)%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20test%20investment-worthy%20luggage%20that%20would%20last%20a%20long%20time%20and%20look%20good%20doing%20it.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72342-20%26h%3Db96f27e39da011c507a04569b002df1c7d14e416ff1a9592584d2786152edbbb%26postID%3D66cf70fa71b62b11ae8c85ff%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftravel%252Fparavel-luggage-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftourparavel.com%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParavel%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20sustainable%20luggage%20brand%20relatively%20new%20to%20the%20scene%20that%20I%20was%20drawn%20to%20aesthetically.%20Learning%20the%20company's%20designs%20are%20made%20of%20100%25%20post-consumer%20recycled%20polycarbonate%20was%20an%20excellent%20bonus.%20So%2C%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20months%20of%20travel%2C%20I%20tested%20the%20brand's%20classic%20suitcase%20and%20carry-on%20bags%20to%20see%20if%20the%20quality%20merited%20the%20upscale%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20specs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20brand%20so%20committed%20to%20sustainable%20construction%2C%20Paravel%20makes%20an%20elegant%2C%20stylish%20suitcase%20that%20feels%20exceptionally%20durable%2C%20too.%20When%20I%20first%20received%20the%20Aviator%20Carry-On%20Plus%20and%20the%20Aviator%20Grand%20Checked%20Luggage%20to%20test%2C%20I%20would%20have%20never%20been%20able%20to%20guess%20that%20its%20materials%20(and%20even%20detailing%20like%20zippers)%20were%20entirely%20recycled.%20A%20striking%20burgundy%20%26quot%3BBoxcar%20Red%26quot%3B%20color%2C%20both%20bags%20have%20a%20classic%20vintage%20aesthetic%20to%20them%20that%20looks%20as%20expensive%20as%20the%20bags%20are.%20(As%20far%20as%20luggage%20goes%2C%20Paravel%20is%20on%20the%20mid-%20to%20higher-end%20side%20of%20things.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20paravel%20suitcases%20in%20front%20of%20a%20door%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf7abd1aa2ac29ee35239d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20carry-on%20and%20checked%20Aviator%20bags%20make%20an%20attractive%20luggage%20pair.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20City-based%20brand%2C%20which%20has%20only%20been%20around%20since%202016%2C%20uses%20100%25%20post-consumer%20recycled%20polycarbonate%20sourced%20from%20discarded%20items%20like%20water%20cooler%20tanks%20and%20CD%20jewel%20cases.%20Paravel%20claims%20to%20have%20recycled%20and%20transformed%20over%207.5%20million%20plastic%20water%20bottles%20into%20their%20stylish%20luggage.%20Another%20cool%20%E2%80%94%20and%20completely%20unique%20%E2%80%94%20sustainability%20feature%20is%20that%20Paravel%20offsets%20the%20carbon%20emissions%20it%20takes%20to%20create%20and%20ship%20your%20purchase%20to%20you%20and%20%3Cem%3Ethen%3C%2Fem%3E%20offsets%20the%20estimated%20emissions%20of%20your%20luggage's%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20trip%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20top%20view%20of%20two%20paravel%20luggage%20pieces%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf7bdd1aa2ac29ee352465%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20the%20carry-on%20and%20checked%20sizes%20feature%20the%20same%20vintage-style%20detailing.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Aviator%20Carry-On%20Plus%20and%20the%20Aviator%20Grand%20Checked%20Luggage%20come%20with%20interior%20compression%20boards%20to%20help%20flatten%20your%20items%20and%20create%20more%20space%2C%20plus%20TSA-approved%20locks%20to%20keep%20everything%20safe.%20They%20also%20both%20feature%20%26quot%3B360-degree%20wheels%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20steel%20axles%20and%20carbon%20steel%20bearings%2C%20designed%20to%20roll%20smoothly%20in%20any%20direction%20and%20turn%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it's%20like%20to%20use%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20Aviator%20Checked%20Luggage%20on%20two%20trips%20%E2%80%94%20one%20domestic%20(lasting%20five%20days)%2C%20and%20one%20international%20(lasting%20eight%20days).%20As%20a%20vehement%20carry-on%20purist%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20ordinarily%20check%20a%20bag%20for%20a%20five-day%20trip%2C%20but%20I%20needed%20to%20pack%20multiple%20outfits%2C%20jewelry%2C%20and%20makeup%20for%20a%20weeklong%20wedding.%20Using%20the%20fasteners%20and%20the%20interior%20compression%20board%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20just%20how%20much%20I%20could%20comfortably%20cram%20into%20the%20suitcase%2C%20and%20it%20kept%20everything%20tightly%20in%20place%3A%20I%20arrived%20at%20my%20hotel%20with%20everything%20exactly%20how%20I'd%20packed%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20the%20Carry-On%20Plus%2C%20I%20packed%20it%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20books%20and%20clothing%20I'd%20planned%20on%20donating%20and%20rolled%20it%20around%20my%20apartment%2C%20up%20and%20down%20my%20stairs%2C%20and%20around%20the%20block.%20The%20Carry-On%20Plus%20has%20the%20same%20design%20and%20organizational%20features%20as%20the%20Checked%20Luggage%2C%20but%20is%20just%20smaller%20in%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20fully%20packed%20paravel%20suitcase%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf7d3c1aa2ac29ee3525bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20Paravel%20luggage%20packed%20to%20the%20brim%20on%20a%20recent%20trip.%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20construction%20perspective%2C%20the%20most%20impressive%20feature%20of%20both%20Paravel%20bags%20is%20the%20wheels%2C%20which%20glided%20across%20both%20the%20airport%20floor%20and%20city%20sidewalks%20like%20butter%20(no%20matter%20how%20much%20I%20overpacked.)%20The%20bags%20have%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20spinner%20wheels%26quot%3B%20that%20smoothly%20roll%20360%20degrees%20in%20any%20direction.%20While%20dragging%20the%20Carry-On%20Plus%20down%20my%20bumpy%20and%20uneven%20Brooklyn%20sidewalk%2C%20the%20wheels%20easily%20handled%20the%20extra%20friction%20and%20continued%20to%20roll%20smoothly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recycled%20polycarbonate%20exterior%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bscuff-hiding%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20mostly%20true%2C%20though%20I%20noticed%20a%20few%20small%20scuffs%20after%20my%20first%20trip%20with%20the%20Grand%20Checked%20Luggage.%20But%20more%20impressive%20to%20me%20is%20that%20after%20two%20big%20vacations%20with%20the%20big%20suitcase%2C%20the%20wheels%20still%20rolled%20as%20smoothly%20as%20when%20I%20first%20tested%20it%2C%20and%20the%20zippers%20showed%20no%20sign%20of%20strain%2C%20even%20though%20I%20completely%20overpacked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20it's%20so%20easy%20to%20organize%20the%20times%20I%20put%20in%20my%20bag%2C%20unpacking%20was%20a%20breeze.%20Usually%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20trip%2C%20I%20give%20up%20on%20organization%20and%20the%20inside%20of%20my%20suitcase%20looks%20like%20a%20giant%20laundry%20pile.%20But%20with%20a%20removable%20laundry%20bag%2C%20two%20smart%20pockets%2C%20and%20the%20compression%20board%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20keep%20everything%20in%20its%20pace%20throughout%20the%20trip%2C%20which%20included%20a%20bunch%20of%20mini%20trips%20that%20involved%20packing%20and%20unpacking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20makes%20it%20stand%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20image%20of%20a%20hand%20holding%20a%20paravel%20suitcase%20next%20to%20a%20dog%20looking%20at%20the%20camera%20in%20front%20of%20a%20paravel%20suitcase%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf7cb2397a168972022172%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Paravel%20Aviator%20line%20is%20travel%20editor-%20and%20chihuahua-approved%3Cp%3EMaria%20Yagoda%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20luggage%20is%20elegant%20and%20classic-looking%2C%20without%20sacrificing%20durability.%20Even%20better%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20Paravel%20actually%20makes%20good%20on%20its%20sustainability%20claims%20by%20being%20completely%20carbon%20neutral%20since%202020%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20offsetting%20the%20emissions%20from%20your%20first%20trip%20with%20the%20luggage.%20These%20bags%20are%20built%20for%20frequent%20travelers%20who