eg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEyebuydirect's%20prices%20are%20super%20affordable%2C%20but%20if%20you%20have%20a%20strong%20prescription%2C%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20price%20to%20go%20up%20significantly.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20have%20a%20strong%20prescription%20(-8%20for%20both%20eyes)%2C%20so%20high-index%20lenses%20are%20always%20a%20must-have%20when%20I'm%20ordering%20glasses.%20While%20Eyebuydirect's%20claim%20for%20affordable%20glasses%20as%20low%20as%20%246%20is%20true%2C%20it%20doesn't%20apply%20to%20any%20order%20requiring%20a%20lens%20upgrade.%20I%20went%20with%20the%20Hathaway%20frames%2C%20which%20cost%20%2442.%20Adding%201.74%20index%20lenses%20will%20add%20another%20%24110%20or%20more%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20specific%20lens%20type.%20Even%20with%20the%20added%20cost%2C%20Eyebuydirect%20is%20still%20an%20affordable%20option%20for%20people%20with%20stronger%20prescriptions.%20It%20will%20cost%20you%20more%20at%20traditional%20glasses%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20your%20prescription%20requires%20a%20lens%20upgrade%2C%20plenty%20of%20options%20exist.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnce%20you%20put%20your%20prescription%20in%2C%20Eyebuydirect%20will%20recommend%20a%20lens%20index%20for%20you.%20Since%20my%20prescription%20is%20strong%2C%20it's%20recommended%20that%20I%20get%20the%20highest%20index%20lenses%20to%20keep%20them%20from%20being%20very%20thick.%20You'll%20get%20to%20choose%20between%20Transitions%2C%20blue%20light-blocking%20lenses%2C%20clear%20lenses%2C%20sunglasses%2C%20and%20more.%20I%20went%20with%20Kodak%20Clean%26amp%3BClear%20lenses%2C%20which%2C%20admittingly%2C%20is%20the%20most%20expensive%20lens%20upgrade%20at%20%24199.95.%20But%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20well%20worth%20the%20upgrade%20with%20a%20coating%20that%20blocks%20UVs%20and%20is%20scratch-resistant%2C%20smudge-resistant%2C%20water-repellent%2C%20and%20dust-repellent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20part%20of%20the%20shopping%20process%20was%20knowing%20exactly%20what%20I'd%20be%20getting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20other%20online%20sites%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20your%20lens%20index%20or%20features%20like%20blue-light%20blocking%20lenses%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20where%20I've%20received%20glasses%20that%20have%20a%20noticeable%20blue%20glare%20or%20strong%20yellow%20tint.%20I%20wanted%20my%20lenses%20to%20be%20crystal%20clear%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20exactly%20that%20with%20all%20of%20Eyebuydirect's%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20notorious%20for%20ordering%20the%20same%20exact%20frames%20with%20my%20new%20prescription%2C%20but%20Eyebuydirect%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20try%20something%20new.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20are%20so%20many%20great%20options%20on%20Eyebuydirect%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20break%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%20with%20a%20new%20shape%20and%20style.%20If%20you%20can't%20find%20something%20you%20like%20from%20browsing%2C%20I%20recommend%20using%20the%20search%20filters.%20Most%20acetate%20or%20plastic%20frames%20don't%20have%20adjustable%20nose%20bridges%2C%20which%20was%20something%20I%20really%20wanted%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20pair%20that%20worked%20for%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20biggest%20con%20is%20that%20frame%20shapes%20come%20and%20go%20quickly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20styles%20I%20have%20been%20testing%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20is%20no%20longer%20available%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20styles%20I%20tested%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20are%20available%20anymore%20either.%20You%20can%20always%20get%20new%20lenses%20for%20your%20favorite%20frames%2C%20but%20if%20the%20frames%20break%20or%20scratch%2C%20you're%20sadly%20out%20of%20luck.%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20S