R%20(standard%20dynamic%20range)%20mode%20with%20brightness%20set%20to%20about%2050%25.%20(Like%20all%20HDR%20TVs%2C%20the%20QM7%20automatically%20sets%20its%20brightness%20to%20100%25%20in%20HDR%20mode%20to%20ensure%20the%20best%20highlight%20performance.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20various%204K%20Blu-rays%20and%20video%20streams%2C%20HDR%20highlights%20(like%20gunshots%2C%20explosions%2C%20and%20lightning)%20shined%20appropriately%2C%20giving%20bright%20elements%20a%20realistic%20sheen.%20The%20colorful%20underwater%20world%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72339-20%26h%3Db90b9b9ab60aa484cea1f56ace35f83983814d1244b5a1198c607ba434a64164%26postID%3D66ce232a71b62b11ae8ad499%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm7-qled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FAquaman-4K-Ultra-HD-Blu-ray%252Fdp%252FB07GW487ZF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAquaman%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20dazzled%20with%20rich%20saturation%20and%20vibrancy.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72339-20%26h%3D8c2dd99b6e454955f9028e3d25eb009f6b57ea75296280585987d099f182ebcc%26postID%3D66ce232a71b62b11ae8ad499%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Ftcl-qm7-qled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FMad-Max-Ultra-Blu-ray-Digital%252Fdp%252FB01BHKO34U%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMad%20Max%3A%20Fury%20Road%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20was%20also%20a%20particularly%20great%20demo%20of%20the%20TV's%20strengths.%20This%20film%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20titles%20mastered%20with%20highlights%20well%20beyond%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20TV's%20light%20output%20a%20real%20workout.%20The%20results%20were%20an%20explosion%20of%20HDR%20goodness%20during%20the%20flick's%20chaotic%20car%20chases%2C%20with%20bold%20blasts%20of%20orange%20fire%20and%20nearly%20blinding%20pulses%20of%20lightning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20rare%20instances%2C%20the%20TV's%20brightness%20algorithm%20could%20get%20a%20little%20confused.%20I%20ran%20into%20a%20minor%20quirk%20during%20quick%20cuts%20to%20shots%20with%20bright%20white%20text%20on%20black%20backgrounds%2C%20particularly%20when%20watching%20videos%20on%20YouTube.%20During%20these%20instances%2C%20the%20white%20text%20appeared%20way%20too%20bright%20for%20a%20second%20or%20two%20before%20the%20TV%20realized%20its%20mistake%20and%20dimmed%20down%20to%20the%20correct%20level.%20This%20is%20a%20tiny%20flaw%2C%20but%20one%20that%20I%20encountered%20enough%20to%20make%20it%20worth%20mentioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20noticed%20some%20intermittent%20motion%20issues%20when%20watching%20streaming%20content%20on%20certain%20apps.%20Some%20videos%20would%20stutter%20slightly%20here%20and%20there.%20I%20noticed%20this%20when%20streaming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fparamount-plus-streaming-service%5C%22%3EParamount%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fpeacock-tv-streaming-service-app%5C%22%3EPeacock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20never%20when%20streaming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fdisney-plus%5C%22%3EDisney%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20YouTube.%20Likewise%2C%20I%20never%20encountered%20this%20issue%20when%20watching%20cable%20TV%20or%20Blu-ray%20discs.%20The%20stuttering%20could%20be%20a%20result%20of%20app%20stability%20rather%20than%20any%20kind%20of%20motion%20issue%20with%20the%20panel%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221785%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM7%204K%20TV%20displaying%20an%20image%20of%20a%20mountain%20near%20a%20lake.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf31ff43b5e59d16b5e9c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221339%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20colors%20distort%20when%20viewed%20from%20an%20angle.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20QLED%20TVs%20in%20the%20midrange%20class%2C%20the%20QM7's%20viewing%20angles%20leave%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired.%20Though%20not%20the%20worst%20I've%20seen%2C%20sitting%20at%20an%20angle%20causes%20the%20TV's%20colors%20and%20contrast%20to%20distort.%20This%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course%20on%20most%20displays%20of%20this%20type%2C%20so%20to%20get%20better%20off-axis%20performance%20you%20need%20to%20opt%20for%20a%20pricier%20Samsung%20QLED%20or%20an%20OLED.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20pricier%20TVs%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20this%20is%20a%20midrange%20display.%20The%20QM7%20impresses%20within%20that%20context%2C%20but%20overall%20image%20quality%20is%20clearly%20a%20step%20down%20compared%20to%20a%20premium%20set.%20Most%20notably%2C%20the%20QM7's%20picture%20processing%20handles%20lower-quality%20sources%2C%20like%20YouTube%20streams%20and%20cable%20TV%2C%20worse%20than%20displays%20I've%20tested%20from%20more%20expensive%20brands%2C%20like%20Sony%20and%20LG%2C%20which%20offer%20a%20sharper%20and%20cleaner%20image.%20And%20even%20with%20local%20dimming%2C%20the%20QM7%20just%20doesn't%20have%20the%20same%20wow%20factor%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-oled-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%20OLED%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20offer%20thanks%20to%20their%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio.%20Check%20out%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fqled-vs-oled%5C%22%3EQLED%20vs.%20OLED%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%20for%20more%20details%20about%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20each%20panel%20type.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20get%20a%20TV%20that%20looks%20considerably%20better%20than%20the%20QM7%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20more%20cash.%20Even%20entry-level%20OLED%20TVs%20cost%20at%20least%20%24600%20more%20than%20what%20the%2065-inch%20QM7%20typically%20sells%20for.%20Considering%20its%20price%2C%20the%20QM7%20is%20a%20picture-quality%20winner%2C%20with%20only%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestbuy.com%2Fsite%2Fhisense-65-class-u7-series-mini-led-4k-uhd-qled-google-tv-2024%2F6577010.p%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHisense%20U7N%3C%2Fa%3E%20posing%20any%20direct%20competition%20in%20its%20price%20range.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20interface%5C%22%3ESnappy%20smart%20TV%20navigation%20but%20there%20are%20some%20glitches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221557%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM7%20TV%20with%20the%20Google%20TV%20interface%20on%20the%20display%20highlighting%20%26quot%3BHouse%20of%20the%20Dragon.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf35d2397a16897201ec14%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221167%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Google%20TV%20interface%20works%20well%20and%20is%20easy%20to%20browse.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETCL's%20QM7%20uses%20the%20Google%20TV%20OS%20(operating%20system)%2C%20and%20though%20I%20encountered%20a%20couple%20of%20hiccups%2C%20it%20offers%20a%20smooth%20smart%20TV%20experience.%20I%20still%20favor%20Roku's%20design%20the%20most%2C%20but%20Google's%20interface%20is%20my%20second%20favorite%20of%20the%20current%20crop%20used%20by%20most%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20homepage%20offers%20rows%20of%20icons%20for%20top-pick%20recommendations%20and%20all%20your%20apps%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20continue-watching%20row%20with%20content%20you've%20started%20but%20haven't%20finished%20and%20additional%20rows%20with%20more%20suggestions%20across%20different%20categories.%20It's%20a%20basic%20setup%20but%20feels%20a%20bit%20more%20streamlined%20and%20user-friendly%20than%20similar%20interfaces%20from%20Amazon%2C%20LG%2C%20and%20Samsung.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20TV%20performance%20can%20vary%20a%20lot%20across%20different%20display%20models%20based%20on%20their%20processing%20power%20and%20each%20manufacturer's%20implementation%20of%20the%20OS%2C%20so%20it's%20great%20to%20see%20such%20speedy%20navigation%20from%20a%20midrange%20set%20like%20this.%20I%20didn't%20run%20into%20many%20instances%20of%20lag%20while%20browsing%20through%20apps%2C%20but%20I%20did%20encounter%20some%20slow-down%20when%20watching%204K%20HDR%20videos%20through%20the%20YouTube%20app.%20Likewise%2C%20pulling%20up%20the%20TV's%20picture%20settings%20menu%20could%20cause%20a%20slight%20delay.%20However%2C%20general%20use%20across%20various%20menus%20is%20snappy.%20Google%20Assistant%20voice%20control%20also%20works%20well%2C%20whether%20using%20the%20remote%20or%20hands-free%20option%20with%20a%20wake%20word.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20downside%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20minor%20glitches%20popped%20up%20during%20my%20testing%2C%20but%20nothing%20too%20egregious.%20One%20instance%20involved%20picture%20brightness%20adjustments%20I%20made%20in%20SDR%20mode%20carrying%20over%20to%20Dolby%20Vision%20mode%2C%20which%20shouldn't%20happen.%20Another%20glitch%20occurred%20when%20the%20TV%20suddenly%20stopped%20outputting%20audio%20to%20my%20soundbar.%20Restarting%20both%20devices%20didn't%20fix%20this%20but%20unplugging%20the%20TV%20and%20then%20turning%20it%20back%20on%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20hate%20how%20the%20Google%20TV%20OS%20stops%20playback%20in%20certain%20streaming%20apps%20when%20you%20open%20the%20picture%20settings%20menu%20to%20make%20changes.%20This%20makes%20it%20impossible%20to%20see%20how%20the%20settings%20you%20adjust%20affect%20the%20picture%20in%20real%20time.%20This%20isn't%20unique%20to%20TCL%20models%20as%20I've%20seen%20it%20happen%20on%20other%20Google%20TVs.%20It%20only%20occurs%20with%20certain%20apps%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20seemingly%20unnecessary%20limitation%20that%20I%20hope%20Google%20changes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Gaming%20features%5C%22%3ESmooth%20144Hz%20gaming%20on%20a%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221747%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM7%20QLED%20TV%20with%20Spider-Man%20on%20PS5%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen%20with%20the%20gaming%20bar%20menu%20pulled%20up.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf28e043b5e59d16b5e4d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20QM7's%20gaming%20bar%20displays%20info%20about%20refresh%20rate%20and%20VRR.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QM7%20is%20well-equipped%20for%20gaming%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20affordable%20QLEDs%20with%20full%204K%2F144Hz%20variable%20refresh%20rate%20(VRR)%20support.%20This%20means%20you%20can%20pair%20the%20TV%20with%20a%20gaming%20PC%20to%20sync%20high-frame-rate%20gameplay%20with%20the%20display's%20refresh%20rate%2C%20ensuring%20smooth%20motion%20while%20preventing%20stuttering%20or%20screen%20tearing.%20The%20TV's%20VRR%20function%20also%20works%20with%20a%20PS5%20or%20Xbox%20Series%20X%2C%20but%20those%20systems%20are%20limited%20to%204K%2F120Hz%20signals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuto%20low%20latency%20mode%20(ALLM)%20is%20also%20supported.%20This%20feature%20automatically%20engages%20the%20QM7's%20game%20mode%20to%20minimize%20input%20lag%20when%20it%20detects%20a%20gaming%20source.%20Like%20many%20midrange%20and%20high-end%20TVs%2C%20the%20QM7%20has%20a%20handy%20pop-up%20gaming%20bar%20that%20displays%20helpful%20information%2C%20like%20the%20current%20refresh%20rate%2C%20and%20offers%20quick%20access%20to%20advanced%20settings.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20TV's%20gaming%20performance%20with%20a%20few%20PS5%20titles%2C%20including%20Marvel's%20Spider-Man%2C%20Ghost%20of%20Tsushima%2C%20and%20The%20Last%20of%20Us%20Part%20I.%20The%20display's%20120Hz%20VRR%20feature%20engaged%20correctly%20when%20playing%20compatible%20titles%2C%20resulting%20in%20smooth%20motion%20and%20unlocked%20frame%20rates.%20High-dynamic-range%20performance%20was%20also%20great%2C%20giving%20the%20city%20lights%20of%20New%20York%20City%20some%20extra%20pop%20in%20Spider-Man%20and%20offering%20gorgeous%20colors%20across%20the%20varied%20landscapes%20of%20Ghost%20of%20Tsushima.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20screen%20tearing%2C%20games%20didn't%20look%20quite%20as%20crisp%20on%20the%20QM7%20as%20they%20have%20on%20competing%20OLED%20TVs%20or%20Samsung%20QLEDs%20that%20I've%20tested.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20slightly%20blurry%20quality%20in%20motion%2C%20but%20not%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20it%20ever%20detracted%20from%20my%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20TCL%20QM7%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221853%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20a%20TCL%20QM7%20QLED%20TV%20with%20an%20image%20of%20town%20with%20the%20Norther%20Lights%20shimmering%20above.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf4436397a16897201fd38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221390%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20on%20sale%20for%20under%20%241%2C000%2C%20the%2065-inch%20QM7%20delivers%20fantastic%20value.%3Cp%3ESteven%20Cohen%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20midrange%20displays%20go%2C%20the%20TCL%20QM7%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-4k-tv%5C%22%3Ebest%204K%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20can%20buy%20right%20now.%20It%20delivers%20solid%20contrast%20and%20snappy%20smart%20TV%20navigation%2C%20along%20with%20all%20the%20latest%20gaming%20features%20you%20could%20wan