to%20assassinate%20Donald%20Trump%20spent%20months%20researching%20him%2C%20along%20with%20other%20targets%20like%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20before%20deciding%20to%20shoot%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20the%20FBI%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftrump-gunman-spent-months-researching-potential-targets-including-joe-biden-before-assassination-attempt-13204961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Student%20Suicide%20Rate%20Surpasses%20Population%20Growth%20Rate%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIncidents%20of%20student%20suicides%20in%20India%20have%20grown%20at%20an%20alarming%20annual%20rate%2C%20surpassing%20the%20population%20growth%20rate%20and%20overall%20suicide%20trends%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20data%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BStudent%20suicides%3A%20An%20epidemic%20sweeping%20India%26quot%3B%20report%20was%20launched%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20Annual%20IC3%20Conference%20and%20Expo%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20overall%20suicide%20numbers%20increased%20by%202%20per%20cent%20annually%2C%20student%20suicides%20cases%20surged%20by%204%20per%20cent%2C%20despite%20a%20likely%20%26quot%3Bunder%20reporting%26quot%3B%20of%20student%20suicide%20cases.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20student%20suicides%20have%20grown%20at%20an%20alarming%20annual%20rate%20of%204%20per%20cent%2C%20double%20the%20national%20average.%20In%202022%2C%20male%20students%20constituted%2053%20pc%20(per%20cent)%20of%20the%20total%20student%20suicides.%20Between%202021%20and%202022%2C%20male%20student%20suicides%20decreased%20by%206%20per%20cent%20while%20female%20student%20suicides%20increased%20by%207%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20the%20report%20compiled%20by%20IC3%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20incidence%20of%20student%20suicides%20continues%20to%20surpass%20both%20population%20growth%20rates%20and%20overall%20suicide%20trends.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20while%20the%20population%20of%200-24-year-olds%20reduced%20from%20582%20million%20to%20581%20million%2C%20the%20number%20of%20student%20suicides%20increased%20from%206%2C654%20to%2013%2C044%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IC3%20Institute%20is%20a%20volunteer-based%20organisation%20that%20provides%20support%20to%20high%20schools%20around%20the%20world%20through%20guidance%20and%20training%20resources%20for%20their%20administrators%2C%20teachers%20and%20counsellors%20to%20help%20establish%20and%20maintain%20robust%20career%20and%20college%20counselling%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20identified%20as%20the%20states%20with%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20student%20suicides%2C%20together%20accounting%20for%20one-third%20of%20the%20national%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouthern%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20collectively%20contribute%2029%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20cases%2C%20while%20Rajasthan%2C%20known%20for%20its%20high-stakes%20academic%20environment%2C%20ranks%2010th%2C%20highlighting%20the%20intense%20pressure%20associated%20with%20coaching%20hubs%20like%20Kota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20data%20compiled%20by%20the%20NCRB%20is%20based%20on%20police-recorded%20first%20information%20reports%20(FIRs).%20However%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20the%20actual%20number%20of%20student%20suicides%20is%20likely%20underreported.%20This%20under-reporting%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20the%20social%20stigma%20surrounding%20suicide%20and%20the%20criminalisation%20of%20attempted%20and%20assisted%20suicide%20under%20Section%20309%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%202017%20Mental%20Healthcare%20Act%20decriminalises%20suicide%20attempts%20for%20individuals%20with%20mental%20illness%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20criminalisation%20continues%20to%20impact%20reporting%20practices%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoreover%2C%20there%20are%20significant%20data%20discrepancies%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20robust%20data%20collection%20system%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20where%20reporting%20is%20less%20consistent%20compared%20to%20urban%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanesh%20Kohli%2C%20the%20Founder%20of%20the%20IC3%20Movement%2C%20said%20the%20report%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%20address%20mental%20health%20challenges%20within%20our%20learning%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20educational%20focus%20must%20shift%20to%20fostering%20the%20competencies%20of%20our%20learners%20such%20that%20it%20supports%20their%20overall%20well-being%2C%20versus%20pushing%20them%20to%20compete%20amongst%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20that%20we%20build%20a%20systematic%2C%20comprehensive%2C%20and%20robust%20career%20and%20college%20counselling%20system%20within%20each%20institution%2C%20while%20seamlessly%20integrating%20the%20same%20within%20the%20learning%20curriculum%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20report%20noted%20a%20dramatic%20increase%20in%20student%20suicides%2C%20with%20male%20suicides%20rising%20by%2050%20per%20cent%20and%20female%20suicides%20by%2061%20per%20cent%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20genders%20have%20experienced%20an%20average%20annual%20increase%20of%205%20pc%20(per%20cent)%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20These%20alarming%20statistics%20underscore%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20enhanced%20counseling%20infrastructure%20and%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20student%20aspirations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAddressing%20these%20gaps%20is%20essential%20for%20shifting%20the%20focus%20from%20competitive%20pressures%20to%20nurturing%20core%20competencies%20and%20well-%20being%2C%20thereby%20supporting%20students%20more%20effectively%20and%20preventing%20such%20tragedies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724868000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2F89btp3lg_suicide-generic_625x300_18_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-student-suicide-rate-surpasses-population-growth-rate-report-6440018%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Incidents%20of%20student%20suicides%20in%20India%20have%20grown%20at%20an%20alarming%20annual%20rate%2C%20surpassing%20the%20population%20growth%20rate%20and%20overall%20suicide%20trends%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fandango%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Story%20of%20Frank%20and%20Nina%E2%80%99%20Debuts%20Clip%20Ahead%20of%20Venice%20Premiere%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724867656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FThe-Story-of-Frank-and-Nina.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236121241%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paola%20Randi%E2%80%99s%20coming-of-age%20drama%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Story%20of%20Frank%20and%20Nina%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20has%20its%20world%20premiere%20in%20Venice%20Film%20Festival%E2%80%99s%20Horizons%20Extra%20program%2C%20has%20debuted%20a%20first%20clip%20(below).%20International%20distribution%20is%20being%20handled%20by%20Fandango%2