Cp%3ESalva%E2%80%99s%20racing%20career%20began%20in%202018%20with%20Formula%20LGB%20in%20India%2C%20and%20she%20quickly%20made%20a%20name%20for%20herself.%20Her%20most%20notable%20achievement%20came%20in%20the%202023%20F4%20UAE%20Championship%2C%20where%20she%20completed%20150%20laps%2C%20a%20number%20that%20speaks%20volumes%20of%20her%20resilience.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMotorsports%20are%20physically%20and%20mentally%20demanding%2C%20with%20challenges%20even%20greater%20for%20women.%20Salva%20shares%20that%20the%20intense%20conditions%20include%2040%C2%B0C%20temperatures%20inside%20the%20car%20and%2060-100%20kg%20braking%20pressure%20during%20curves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20body%20types%20and%20energy%20levels%20affect%20our%20endurance%20capacity.%20One%20loses%20around%204%20kg%20of%20body%20weight%20during%20the%20races.%20A%20racer%20needs%20the%20physique%20of%20a%20fighter%20pilot%2C%20including%20quick%20reflexes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Despite%20setbacks%20like%20crashes%20and%20spins%2C%20Salva%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335635%2Fnarain-karthikeyan-india-first-f1-driver-entrepreneur-drivex-mobility-refurbished-two-wheelers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20passion%20and%20ability%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20experience%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20kept%20her%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20as%20Salva%20prepares%20to%20join%20the%20Formula%201%20Academy%20in%20January%202025%2C%20she%20stands%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20history.%20Qualifying%20for%20the%20academy%20would%20not%20only%20alleviate%20her%20financial%20burdens%20but%20also%20cement%20her%20place%20in%20the%20global%20racing%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalva%E2%80%99s%20ultimate%20goal%20is%20clear%3A%20to%20represent%20India%20in%20Formula%201%20and%20inspire%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20female%20racers.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20female%20athlete%2C%20I%20am%20particularly%20motivated%