0can%20help%20in%20crime%20prevention%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Harssh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20mission%20of%20MARVEL%20is%20to%20augment%2C%20not%20replace%2C%20human%20law%20enforcement.%20Seasoned%20officers%2C%20like%20head%20constables%20or%20inspectors%2C%20assess%20large%20volumes%20of%20data%20and%20provide%20valuable%20insights%20based%20on%20the%20patterns%20they%20recognise.%20This%20entity%20would%20perform%20these%20tasks%20too%2C%20once%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20data%20has%20been%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20proliferation%20of%20technology%20in%20urban%20spaces%E2%80%94such%20as%20the%20widespread%20use%20of%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20mobile%20phones%2C%20which%20frequently%20capture%20photos%20and%20videos%E2%80%94many%20crimes%20are%20now%20recorded%20digitally.%20AI%20algorithms%20can%20analyse%20this%20visual%20data%20to%20predict%20and%20prevent%20crimes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20detect%20them%20after%20they%20occur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20an%20example%20of%20chain%20snatching%20cases%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20rural%20SP%20states%20that%20the%20role%20of%20AI%20can%20be%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAI%20might%20notice%20details%20in%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20that%20a%20human%20might%20miss%2C%20such%20as%20the%20specific%20make%20of%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20it%20travels%2C%20or%20the%20type%20of%20helmet%20used%20by%20the%20perpetrator.%20These%20subtle%20patterns%20can%20be%20crucial%20in%20solving%20cases%20and%20preventing%20future%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20states%20too%20might%20be%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20augment%20law%20enforcement%2C%20Maharashtra%20might%20be%20the%20first%20to%20create%20an%20independent%20entity%20for%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20role%20of%20MARVEL%20is%20not%20to%20provide%20solutions%20on%20a%20case%20to%20case%20basis.%20Instead%2C%20it%20focuses%20on%20developing%20tools%20and%20algorithms%20that%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20can%20deploy%20in%20their%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F284171%2Fpolice-inspector-teaches-poor-children-ayodhya-inspiration-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENagpur%20Rural%20SP%20%3C%2Fa%3Estates%20that%20if%20a%20particular%20police%20team%20wants%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20deal%20with%20cases%20of%20missing%20people%2C%20and%20share%20their%20requirements%2C%20MARVEL%20would%20design%20it%20and%20share%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20an%20investigative%20agency%20that%20is%20providing%20help%20with%20particular%20cases.%20We%20would%20design%20a%20tool%20depending%20upon%20the%20requirement%20of%20the%20other%20agency%20and%20then%20we%20would%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20stresses%20Harrsh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20AI%20can%20solve%20complex%20crimes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20MARVEL%20is%20working%20on%20five%20different%20projects%20for%20as%20many%20agencies.%20It%20has%2025%20technical%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20AI%20tools%20will%20be%20able%20to%20layer%20data%20and%20give%20a%20fair%20sense%20of%20what%20might%20have%20happened.%20It%20would%20give%20predictive%20modelling%20solutions%2C%20which%20officials%20will%20then%20have%20to%20interpret.%20It%20will%20show%20you%20trends%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Sujata%20Saunik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-55-min-1724677529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22ht