ockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrushed%20under%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20world%20and%20gradually%20spiralling%20into%20depression%2C%20Nirmala%20found%20solace%20and%20strength%20in%20her%20mother%2C%20brother%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sister-in-law)%2C%20who%20became%20her%20pillars%20of%20support.%20Drawing%20from%20their%20encouragement%2C%20she%20began%20working%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmala%2C%20who%20was%20married%20off%20young%20and%20had%20no%20business%20skills%2C%20began%20making%20and%20selling%20traditional%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%3C%2Fem%3E%20snacks.%20Though%20hesitant%20at%20first%2C%20she%20knew%20that%20the%20situation%20demanded%20her%20to%20step%20up%20and%20become%20financially%20independent.%20She%20wanted%20to%20give%20her%20three%20kids%20the%20life%20that%20they%20deserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20set%20off%20on%20her%20journey%20to%20win%20over%20life%E2%80%99s%20adversities%2C%20Nirmala%20faced%20both%20cheers%20and%20taunts%20from%20those%20around%20her.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307848%2Fpurvina-virgin-coconut-oil-business-by-kerala-mother-daughter-duo-ventha-velichennal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUndeterred%2C%20she%2C%20along%20with%20her%20mother%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20continued%20to%20expand%20their%20business.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Today%2C%20Marwadi%20Manwar%20offers%20over%20150%20varieties%20of%20Rajasthani%20snacks%2C%20a%20testament%20to%20their%20hard%20work%20and%20dedication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERooted%20in%20age-old%20recipes%2C%20the%20venture%20now%20employs%2030%20women%20and%20is%20making%20waves%20on%20e-commerce%20platforms%2C%20both%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20What%20started%20with%20a%20modest%20order%20worth%20Rs%20150%20now%20reaches%20up%20to%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20per%20month%20during%20the%20festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmala%20credits%20the%20success%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20%3C