n%20cover%20was%20gradually%20reducing.%20I%20was%20depressed%20and%20wished%20to%20utilise%20my%20time%20in%20a%20productive%20manner%20post%20work.%20I%20put%20out%20a%20Facebook%20post%20in%202019%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20plant%20saplings%20and%20people%20were%20welcome%20to%20join%2C%E2%80%9D%20Angshuman%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20was%20overwhelmingly%20positive%20and%20led%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%20whose%20first%20agenda%20was%20planting%2050%20saplings%20on%205%20June%202019.%20Being%20on%20the%20ground%20led%20to%20several%20interactions%20with%20locals%20and%20students.%20The%20teacher%20took%20some%20of%20them%20under%20his%20wings%20and%20would%20solve%20their%20doubts%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20former%20students%20hailed%20from%20a%20village%20called%20Samlapur%20in%20Farakka%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20visit%20their%20village.%20It%20was%20after%20the%20first%20lockdown%20that%20the%20teacher%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20and%20he%20was%20astonished%20by%20what%20he%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20setting%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329929%2Farchana-nooguri-headmistress-government-school-national-teachers-award-enrollment-dropout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%20matched%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20beautiful%20and%20lush%20green.%20I%20had%20been%20meaning%20to%20start%20a%20school%20for%20children%2C%20and%20seeing%20the%20village%20and%20its%20children%20gave%20me%20the%20push%20I%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20financial%20backing%2C%20constructing%20four%20walls%20for%20a%20school%20was%20also%20not%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tribal%20hamlet%2C%20Samlapur%20housed%20first%20generation%20learners%2C%20who%20were%20severely%20affected%20by%20schools%20shutting%20down.%20Their%20parents%2C%20who%20were%20daily%20wage%20workers%2C%20had%20no%20work%20and%20their%20worsening%20economic%20situations%20forced%20the%20children%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudents%20were%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20mid-day%20meals.%20The%20students%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Adivasi%20families%20are%20extremely%20marginalised.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20continue%20their%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20Farakka%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20age%20Santiniketan%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnirvana%20Gacher%20Iskul%2C%20an%20open%20air%20school%20under%20the%20shades%20of%20trees%20was%20born%20in%202021%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20school%20to%20these%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC9jwkvXJXa7%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%20(%40gachgreenhands)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20focus%20in%20the%20beginning%20was%20providing%20them%20basic%20education%20and%20meals.%20We%20started%20with%20five%20students%20and%20within%20a%20week%2C%20we%20had%20over%2020%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20Tagore%E2%80%99s%20philosophy%2C%20the%20children%20are%20taught%20under%20neem%20trees%20and%20mango%20trees.%20A%20basic%20sense%20of%20environmental%20awareness%20and%20oneness%20with%20nature%20is%20inoculated.%20Concepts%20are%20taught%20by%20correlating%20them%20with%20what%20they%20see%20around%20them%2C%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20merely%20bookish%20knowledge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20his%20own%20experiences%20as%20a%20student%20in%20Visva%20Bharathi%20university%2C%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20focuses%20on%20learning%20in%20sync%20with%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20studied%20in%20the%20open%2C%20under%20trees%20in%20Santiniketan%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20nature%20and%20culture.%20Unlike%20other%20colleges%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20is%20only%20on%20textbooks%20and%20curriculum%2C%20we%20are%20taught%20to%20be%20one%20with%20nature.%20Our%20creativity%20is%20enhanced%20and%20out%20of%20the%20box%20thinking%20is%20encouraged%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Anirvana%20school%20too%2C%20children%20are%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20drawing%2C%20artwork%2C%20dance%2C%20music%20and%20sports.%20Professional%20artists%20visit%20the%20school%20and%20teach%20the%20children%20simple%20clay%20modelling%20and%20other%20art%20forms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20children%20are%20naturally%20very%20creative%20and%20very%20good%20at%20drawing%20and%20clay%20model%20making.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20explore%20their%20talent%20with%20locally%20available%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20children%20are%20taught%20art%2C%20craft%20and%20culture%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-52-min-1724074343-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20children%20are%20taught%20art%2C%20craft%20and%20culture%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20schools%20reopened%2C%20the%20school%20continued%20to%20function%20before%20school%20hours.%20School%20starts%20at%206%3A30%20am%20and%20provides%20breakfast.%20They%20follow%20the%20government%20curriculum%2C%20but%20with%20a%20twist.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20teach%20them%20poems%2C%20stories%2C%20history%20from%20their%20syllabus%20with%20live%20examples%20found%20in%20nature.%20We%20help%20them%20relate%20whatever%20we%20teach%20with%20native%20examples.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20they%20are%20learning%20about%20flowers%2C%20we%20try%20to%20show%20them%20whatever%20followers%20are%20locally%20available%20which%20improves%20their%20understanding%20and%20leads%20to%20an%20appreciation%20of%20their%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20teach%20this%20way%2C%20without%20poring%20over%20the%20books.%20Seeing%20the%20success%20of%20the%20school%2C%20the%20village%20%3Cem%3Emukhiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(head)%20gave%20them%20the%20community%20centre%2C%20where%20classes%20are%20conducted%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20ahead%2C%20Angshuman%20hopes%20to%20purchase%20some%20land%20and%20set%20up%20a%20school%20with%20an%20eco-friendly%20campus.%20He%20also%20wishes%20to%20set%20up%20a%20computer%20lab%20and%20library%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20this%20initiative%20and%20the%20children%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20improve%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20village.%20We%20are%20sowing%20the%20seeds%20of%20entrepreneurship%20in%20these%20children%2C%20which%20will%20reach%20the%20community%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Angshuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296463%2Fjharkhand-teacher-sapan-patralekh-teaches-parents-and-grandparents-improves-literacy-rate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20currently%20has%20105%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20kindergarten%20to%20Class%2012%20and%20seven%20teachers.%20It%20costs%20Rs%20300%20per%20child%20per%20month%2C%20which%20is%20Rs%203%2C600%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20support%20a%20child%20by%20donating%20through%20UPI%20on%207001714095%40axl%20or%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccount%20no%3A%2041165791703%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EName%3A%20Gach%20Green%20Hands%20Social%20Welfare%20Trust%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIFSC%3A%20SBIN0018784%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pad