e%20years%2C%20its%20founder%20Laljibhai%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F317569%2Fharyana-startup-senior-citizen-travel-vacation-plan-seniorworld-redefine-ageing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eray%20of%20hope%20for%20many%20senior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20abandoned%20by%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Chandrakant%20Navinbhai%20Gajjar.%20Long%20hours%20spent%20weaving%20left%20Chandrakant%20blind.%20When%20he%20turned%20to%20his%20family%20for%20support%2C%20he%20did%20not%20find%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20started%20ignoring%20me%2C%20causing%20frustration%20and%20social%20isolation.%20It%20became%20unbearable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20In%202017%2C%20Chandrakant%E2%80%99s%20brother%20introduced%20him%20to%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20where%20he%20says%20he%20found%20dignity%20at%20long%20last.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20provided%20me%20with%20good%20care%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Medicines%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20a%20comfortable%20atmosphere%20are%20provided%20to%20the%20senior%20citizens%20at%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMedicines%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20a%20comfortable%20atmosphere%20are%20provided%20to%20the%20senior%20citizens%20at%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Himanshu%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senior%20citizens%20from%20across%20Kachchh%20find%20solace%20in%20the%20old%20age%20home%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-3_11zon-1723031383-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenior%20citizens%20from%20across%20Kachchh%20find%20solace%20in%20the%20old%20age%20home%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Himanshu%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20heartwarming%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Devji%20Keshabhai%20Maheshwari%20who%20lost%20his%20mother%20at%20a%20young%20age%20and%20lived%20with%20his%20father%20and%20stepmother.%20While%20Devji%E2%80%99s%20eyesight%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20good%20since%20childhood%2C%20it%20worsened%20as%20he%20got%20older.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20his%20relatives%20for%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20helped%20him%20connect%20with%20Laljibhai%E2%80%99s%20trust.%20Here%2C%20Devji%20says%20he%20received%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139806%2Fsaroja-banappa-86-years-old-crowdfund-old-age-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecare%20and%20support%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20had%20been%20deprived%20of%20for%20years.%20%E2%80%9CI%20receive%20all%20the%20necessary%20facilities%20including%20food%2C%20medicine%2C%20clothing%2C%20and%20footwear.%20I%20feel%20grateful%20to%20all%20those%20who%20are%20making%20the%20old%20age%20home%20a%20great%20place%20for%20people%20like%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20initially%2C%20there%20was%20only%20a%20single%20old%20age%20home%20operational%20for%20blind%20people%2C%20in%202003%2C%20the%20trust%20founded%20another%20one%20for%20non-disabled%20elderly%20people%20who%20lost%20their%20children%20in%20the%202001%20Bhuj%20earthquake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBeyond%20an%20old%20age%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Laljibhai%20saw%20the%20Mandal%20getting%20radical%20acceptance%20from%20the%20Government%20and%20society%20%E2%80%94%20in%202006%2C%20the%20trust%20was%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20National%20Award%20for%20%E2%80%98Creation%20of%20Barrier-free%20Environment%20for%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%E2%80%99%20by%20Dr%C2%A0%20A%20P%20J%20Abdul%20Kalam%2C%20then%20President%20of%20India%20%E2%80%94%20he%20decided%20to%20extend%20its%20reach%20to%20the%20youth%20and%20young%20children%20too.%20Every%20activity%20at%20the%20trust%20is%20laced%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20agency%20back%20to%20disabled%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20trust%E2%80%99s%20most%20successful%20initiatives%20is%20the%20inclusive%20education%20programme.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20unique%20school%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333887%2Fsangopita-shelter-home-disabled-children-cerebral-palsy-autism-adhd%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20with%20various%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20visual%2C%20intellectual%2C%20hearing%2C%20and%20locomotion%20%E2%80%94%20are%20taught%2C%E2%80%9D%20Laljibhai%20explains.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20programme%20ensures%20that%20these%20students%20are%20included%20in%20the%20mainstream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20inclusive%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20primary%20boys%20school%2C%20primary%20and%20secondary%20girls%20school%2C%20and%20secondary%20and%20higher%20secondary%20co-ed%20school%20%E2%80%94%20provide%20the%20students%20with%20study%20material%20in%20braille%2C%20audio%20content%2C%20and%20facilities%20such%20as%20libraries%2C%20computer%20labs%20with%20a%20screen%20reader%2C%20smart%20classes%2C%20sports%2C%20yoga%20dance%2C%20and%20music%20classes.%20Laljibhai%20adds%20that%20the%20infrastructure%20is%20such%20that%20these%20students%20can%20learn%20in%20the%20mode%20that%20suits%20them%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20was%20born%20out%20of%20Laljibhai's%20desire%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20elderly%20visually%20impaired%20people%20in%20society%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-4-1723031468.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%